# --- INTENTIONALLY COMMITTED (do NOT ignore) ---
# The dashboard ships with a bundled demo so it works on first launch with
# no downloads. Keep these tracked:
#   kepler.db                 - results metadata (synthetic + Kepler 8-17 +
#                               TOI-132 + Wolf-Rayet stars)
#   data/processed/*.npz      - light-curve arrays + PINN model curves
#   data/spectra/*.npz        - bundled JWST/HST Wolf-Rayet spectra
